name: Handbagmaker
overview: Handbagmaker is a social utility shopping Web site. It offers handbags, including backpacks, clutches, evening, hobos, satchels, totes, and shoulder bags and clothing, such as athletic, bridal, dresses, intimates, jackets, jeans, maternity, outerwear, pants, petites, plus sizes, shorts, skirts, suits, sweaters, tops, and swimwear; We also provides shoes, such as athletic, evening, flats, mules and clogs, platforms, pumps, sandals, boots, and wedges; and accessories, which include belts, gloves, hair accessories, hats, jewelry, scarves and wraps, sunglasses, and wallets.
